        <updateDate>2021-05-07T16:44:22Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Mens Rea Reform Act of 2021</b> <p>This bill establishes a default <i>mens rea</i> standard (i.e., state of mind requirement) for federal criminal offenses&#8212;statutory and regulatory&#8212;that lack an explicit standard.</p> <p>The government must generally prove that a defendant acted willfully with respect to each element of an offense for which the text does not specify a state of mind. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
